title: Janeane Garofalo - Wikipedia
snippet: Janeane Garofalo (/ dʒəˈniːn ɡəˈrɒfəloʊ / jə-NEEN gə-ROF-əl-oh; born September 28, 1964 [1]) is an American comedian and actress. The accolades she has received include nominations for two Primetime Emmy Awards and a Screen Actors Guild Award.

title: Janeane Garofalo - IMDb
snippet: Janeane Garofalo. Actress: Mystery Men. Janeane, the petite woman with the acerbic wit, was born in Newton, New Jersey, in 1964, to Joan, a secretary, and Carmine Garofalo, an Exxon executive. She is of Italian and Irish descent. Janeane had many jobs before breaking into show biz.
